    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the spring roll wraps have 12 min left, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a little drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>carrot discs</strong> and <strong>halved Tenderstem </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
