    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly softened, add your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>and cook for a final 4-5 min or until tender with a slight bite – this is your <strong>stir-fried veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
